item.g:description: HighlightsKeep up with the action، shooting at 10 fps with Intelligent Tracking and Recognition (iTR) autofocus when using the camera’s optical viewfinder. Bursts at up to 11 fps are possible in Live View mode. Equipped with an enhanced 32. 5 Megapixel CMOS (APS-C) sensor، powerful DIGIC 8 image processor and an ISO range of 100-25000 (expandable to 51200)، you'll achieve sharp، detailed images، even in low-light settings. As a DSLR the EOS 90D features a bright، clear optical viewfinder that shows the world as it really is، in real-time. Perfect for fast-moving subjects، the EOS 90D camera features a 45-point cross-type AF system and EOS iTR AF (face detection) - plus high-speed continuous shooting of up to 10 fps - raising the game for wildlife and motorsports photography enthusiasts. And with stunning uncropped 4K 30p video capability، the EOS 90D documents your travels، events and other milestones in full، wide-angle view. In this kit، the camera is paired with a very versatile EF-S 18-135mm f/3. 5-5. 6 IS USM lens، which is suitable for everything from landscapes to portraits and sport. This Intuitive DSLR is a result of a gradual evolution in design، and feels comfortable to use when shooting with large telephoto lenses and for long periods of time. Keep shooting for longer with a 1،300-shot battery life – great when you’re on location or away from home.
